<item>
            <title>[SPR-100] CustomDateEditor does not allow null date to be converted to text</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-100</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If allowEmpty-flag is true, org.springframework.beans.propertyeditors.CustomDateEditor will properly convert empty string to null value, but if one tries to convert null date to empty String, NPE is thrown.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="10264">SPR-100</key>
            <summary>CustomDateEditor does not allow null date to be converted to text</summary>
